X\sim U([1,3])
EX=\frac{1+3}{2}=2
EX^{2}=\frac{3^{3}-1^{3}}{3}=\frac{8}{3}
\sigma^{2}(X)=\frac{8}{3}-2=\frac{2}{3}
P(S_{300}\leq615.2)=P(\frac{S_{300}-300\cdot2}{\sqrt{300}\cdot\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}}\leq\frac{615.2-300\cdot2}{\sqrt{300}\cdot\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}})=\approx P(X_{0,1}\leq\frac{1.52}{\sqrt{2}})
X_{0,1}\sim N(0,1)
P(S_{300}\geq604)=1-P(S_{300}<604)=1-P(S_{300}\leq604)
